sion, actions within that layer of illusion are required for removing it. I=
t will not magically disappear. After all, yoga vaasishtham emphasizes "act=
ions" in the dual world for realizing non-dual Self. Action and knowledge a=
s the two wings with which the bird of individualized consciousness rises f=
rom the ground of duality to reach the sky of true Self.
 
